WEBVTT

00:01.822 --> 00:06.669
ï»¿I'm a professional cook called a chef of a kitchen I am the head.

00:07.131 --> 00:09.335
Through your stomach, I find my way...

00:09.812 --> 00:12.057
...into your heart is what they say.

00:12.457 --> 00:14.933
In the kitchen all day 'til late, I sweat.

00:15.461 --> 00:17.582
Over the dishes that I cook, I fret.

00:18.115 --> 00:22.957
In aroma, color, texture, and taste, whatever I cook is simply great!

00:23.501 --> 00:25.651
I wear a coat that's usually white.

00:26.114 --> 00:28.315
Apron and a hat that fits me right.

00:28.745 --> 00:33.910
I work mainly behind the scene, so in public I'm rarely seen.

00:34.319 --> 00:39.155
The first course of the meal to the last, I prepare and serve it with class.

00:39.311 --> 00:41.817
From common to exotic dishes,..

00:41.966 --> 00:44.597
...I cook whatever my customer wishes.

